These commands are run from the Control PC once it is connected to the ad-hoc wireless created by the ZBox/Robot on boot.


Term 1
------
source turtle_controlPC_script.sh
rostopic list
rosrun turtlebot_dashboard turtlebot_dashboard&

Once dashboard is running, check battery is displayed.
Then set run mode to full.


Term 2
------
source turtle_controlPC_script.sh
roslaunch turtlebot_teleop keyboard_teleop.launch

Using the keyboard should move the robot


Term 3
------
source turtle_controlPC_script.sh
roslaunch turtlebot_bringup kinect.launch
rosrun rviz rviz

Of course, this only works if kinect is set up
